Class ResponseFromServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.ResponseFromServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class ResponseFromServer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The class contains information about an answer that the server returns to the client. The server creates an answer with all the details the client requested. In addition can add a message in favor of identification. For example, whether the search was successful or not, whether the operation was successful or not, etc.

    Yuval Hayam
